r.com%2Fdemocrats-replacing-biden-with-harris-for-campaign-funds-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EVice%20President%20Kamala%20Harris%3C%2Fa%3E%20may%20be%20the%20most%20obvious%20and%20viable%20option%20for%20Democrats%20given%20the%20immediate%20war%20chest%20she%20would%20get%20from%20Biden's%20campaign%20and%20the%20boost%20from%20intra-party%20support.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fprofessor-predicts-trump-will-win-2016-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAllan%20Lichtman%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20presidential%20historian%20at%20American%20University%2C%20told%20The%20Wall%20Street%20Journal%20that%20even%20Harris%20can't%20save%20the%20Democrats%20based%20on%20his%20famous%20model%2C%20%26quot%3BKeys%20to%20the%20White%20House.%26quot%3B%20This%20model%20entails%2013%20true-and-false%20questions%20to%20determine%20the%20performance%20of%20the%20party%20holding%20the%20White%20House.%20If%20six%20or%20more%20of%20the%2013%20keys%20are%20false%2C%20then%20the%20holding%20party%2C%20in%20this%20case%2C%20the%20Democrats%2C%20will%20lose.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELichtman%20told%20the%20Journal%20that%20Biden%20has%20provided%20Democrats%20with%20seven%20keys%20so%20far%3A%20the%20incumbency%2C%20no%20significant%20primary%20contest%2C%20no%20recession%20during%20the%20election%2C%20a%20strong%20long-term%20economy%20based%20on%20real%20per%20capita%20economic%20growth%20compared%20to%20the%20average%20of%20the%20previous%20two%20terms%2C%20major%20policy%20changes%2C%20no%20major%20scandal%20directly%20pertaining%20to%20the%20president%2C%20and%20an%20uncharismatic%20challenger.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20Harris%20were%20to%20become%20the%20new%20nominee%2C%20Democrats%20risk%20losing%20two%20of%20those%20keys%20Biden%20secured%3A%20the%20incumbency%20and%20the%20primary%20contest.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBiden%20steps%20aside%2C%20they%20lose%20obviously%20the%20incumbency%2C%26quot%3B%20Lichtman%20told%20the%20Jour