a%20Fadnavis%20supported%20Mr%20Shinde's%20claims%2C%20stating%20that%20the%20NDA%20leaders%20did%20not%20pay%20enough%20attention%20to%20the%20lies%20spread%20by%20the%20Opposition%20during%20the%20campaign.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rally%20was%20attended%20by%20leaders%20of%20Shiv%20Sena%2C%20BJP%2C%20NCP%20headed%20by%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20Ajit%20Pawar%2C%20and%20other%20small%20constituents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Maharashtra%2C%20which%20sends%2048%20members%20to%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20the%20BJP-led%20NDA%20could%20win%20only%2017%20seats%2C%20while%20the%20MVA%20comprising%20the%20Congress%2C%20NCP%20(Sharadchandra%20Pawar)%20and%20Shiv%20Sena%20(UBT)%20bagged%2030%20constituencies.%20The%20Independent%20candidate%20who%20won%20the%20Sangli%20constituency%20is%20a%20Congress%20leader.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20were%20caught%20off%20guard%20by%20the%20opposition%20during%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Shinde%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSome%20of%20our%20voters%20went%20on%20holiday%20during%20the%20polling%2C%20assuming%20that%20the%20NDA%20would%20easily%20win%20more%20than%20400%20seats%20in%20the%20general%20elections.%20This%20loss%20underscores%20the%20need%20for%20a%20more%20strategic%20approach%20in%20the%20future%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Shinde%20claimed%20the%20opposition%20voters%20diligently%20exercised%20their%20franchise%2C%20with%20almost%2080%20per%20cent%20turnout.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%2060%20per%20cent%20of%20our%20voters%20had%20turned%20up%20at%20the%20polling%20booths%2C%20we%20could%20have%20easily%20won%2040%20seats.%20We%20can't%20afford%20to%20be%20naive%20or%20callous%20after%20being%20hit%20hard%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20critical%20remark%20against%20Congress%2C%20Mr%20Shinde%20highlighted%20its%20history%20of%20scams%2C%20such%20as%20Bofors%2C%20fodder%2C%20and%20coal%2C%20while%20questioni