hile%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Washington%20Sundar%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F108593-washington-sundar-playerprofile%5C%22%3EWashington%20Sundar%3C%2Fa%3E%20took%20two%20as%20Zimbabwe%20could%20only%20manage%20to%20score%20115%2F9%20in%2020%20overs.%20In%20response%2C%20the%20Indian%20cricket%20team%20batters%20lost%20the%20plot%20completely%20as%20the%20visitors%20kept%20losing%20wickets%20at%20regular%20intervals%20and%20were%20all%20out%20for%20just%20102.%20India%20skipper%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Shubman%20Gill%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F108578-shubman-gill-playerprofile%5C%22%3EShubman%20Gill%3C%2Fa%3E%20criticised%20his%20side's%20fielding%20after%20the%2013-run%20loss%20and%20also%20said%20that%20after%20losing%20five%20wickets%20early%2C%20he%20himself%20should%20have%20stayed%20till%20the%20end%20to%20finish%20the%20match%20for%20his%20side.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20bowled%20pretty%20well%2C%20we%20let%20ourselves%20down%20in%20the%20field.%20We%20were%20not%20up%20to%20standard%20and%20everyone%20looked%20a%20bit%20rusty.%20We%20spoke%20about%20taking%20time%20and%20enjoying%20our%20batting%20but%20it%20didn't%20pan%20out%20that%20way.%20Halfway%20through%20we%20had%20lost%205%20wickets%2C%20would've%20been%20best%20for%20us%20if%20I%20stayed%20there%20till%20the%20end%2C%20very%20disappointed%20with%20the%20way%20I%20got%20out%20and%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20match%20panned%20out.%20There%20was%20a%20bit%20of%20hope%20for%20us%20but%20when%20you're%20chasing%20115%20and%20your%20no.10%20batter%20is%20out%20there%2C%20you%20know%20something%20is%20wrong%2C%26quot%3B%20Gill%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EZimbabwe%20captain%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Sikandar%20Raza%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1569-sikandar-raza-playerprofile%5C%22%3ESikandar%20Raza%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20ecstatic%20with%20his%20team's%20display%20and%20said%20that%20it%20was%20not%20a%20low-scoring%20surface%20and%20it%20was%20the%20calibre%20of%20the%20bowlers%20that%20did%20not%20allow%20the%20batters%20to%20score%20a%20lot%20of%20runs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFeel%20really%20happy%20about%20the%20win.%20Need%20to%20take%20one%20game%20at%20a%20time.%20The%20job%20is%20not%20done%2C%20series%20is%20not%20over.%20World%20champions%20play%20like%20world%20champions%20so%20we%20need%20to%20be%20ready%20for%20the%20next%20game.%20This%20isn't%20a%20wicket%20where%20you%20get%20bowled%20out%20for%20115.%20Credit%20to%20the%20bowlers%20of%20both%20sides.%20Clearly%20an%20indication%20we%20need%20to%20up%20our%20skills.%20I%20said%20I%20don't%20care%20about%20the%20result%20as%20long%20as%20we%20could%20be%20true%20to%20the%20crowd%20and%20changing%20room%2C%20we%20had%20our%20plans%2C%20we%20stuck%20to%20it%20and%20we%20backed%20our%20guys.%20Our%20catching%20and%20ground%20fielding%20was%20amazing%20but%20we%20did%20make%20some%20errors%2C%20shows%20there's%20room%20for%20improvement.%20We%20knew%20the%20fans%20would%20lift%20us%20up%20and%20give%20us%20energy%2C%20credit%20to%20them%2C%20it%20helped%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20Raza%20said%20at%20the%20post-match%20presentation.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720279500000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Fsp5e3vco_x_625x300_06_July_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fzimbabwe-vs-india-2024%2Fnot-up-to-standard-shubman-gills-brutally-honest-take-on-shocking-loss-against-zimbabwe-6048583%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20new-look%20Indian%20cricket%20team%20slumped%20to%20a%20shocking%20loss%20against%20Zimbabwe%20in%20their%20first%20T20I%20encounter%20in%20Harare%20on%20Saturday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fzimbabwe-vs-india-2024%2Fnot-up-to-standard-shubman-gills-brutally-honest-take-on-shocking-loss-against-zimbabwe-6048583%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%