E%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20got%20married%2C%20we%20did%20have%20about%20%2410%2C000%20starting%20off.%20I%20told%20Susie%2C%20%26quot%3BNow%2C%20you%20know%2C%20there's%20two%20choices%2C%20it's%20up%20to%20you.%20We%20can%20either%20buy%20a%20house%2C%20which%20will%20use%20up%20all%20my%20capital%20and%20clean%20me%20out%2C%20and%20it'll%20be%20like%20a%20carpenter%20who's%20had%20his%20tools%20taken%20away%20from%20him.%20Or%20you%20can%20let%20me%20work%20on%20this%20and%20someday%2C%20who%20knows%2C%20maybe%20I'll%20even%20buy%20a%20little%20bit%20larger%20house%20than%20would%20otherwise%20be%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20she%20was%20very%20understanding%20on%20that%20point.%20And%20we%20waited%20until%201956.%20We%20got%20married%20in%201952.%20And%20I%20decided%20to%20buy%20a%20house%20when%20the%20down%20payment%20was%20about%2010%25%20or%20so%20of%20my%20net%20worth%2C%20because%20I%20really%20felt%20I%20wanted%20to%20use%20the%20capital%20for%20other%20purposes.%26quot%3B%20(Buffett%20believed%20he%20could%20invest%20%2431%2C500%20and%20turn%20it%20into%20%241%20million%20in%20about%20a%20dozen%20years%2C%20so%20%26quot%3Bhe%20felt%20as%20though%20he%20were%20spending%20an%20outrageous%20million%20dollars%20on%20the%20house%2C%26quot%3B%20author%20Alice%20Schroeder%20writes%20in%20her%20biography%20of%20Buffett.)%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbuffett.cnbc.com%2Fvideo%2F1998%2F05%2F04%2Fafternoon-session---1998-berkshire-hathaway-annual-meeting.html%3F%26start%3D106.94%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E1998%20meeting%3C%2Fa%3E)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Warren%20Buffett's%20house%20in%20Omaha%2C%20Nebraska.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66881acd268f62ba18a7c707%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22681%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWarren%20Buffett's%20house%20in%20Omaha%2C%20Nebraska.%3Cp%3EJohannes%20Eisele%2FAFP%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BHome%20ownership%20makes%20sense%20for%20most%20Americans.%20The%20third-best%20investment%20I%20ever%20made%20was%20the%20purchase%20of%20my%20home%2C%20though%20I%20would%20have%20made%20far%20more%20money%20had%20I%20instead%20rented%20and%20used%20the%20purchase%20money%20to%20buy%20stocks.%20(The%20two%20best%20investments%20were%20wedding%20rings.)%20For%20the%20%2431%2C500%20I%20paid%20for%20our%20house%2C%20my%20family%20and%20I%20gained%2052%20years%20of%20terrific%20memories%20with%20more%20to%20come.%26quot%3B%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fberkshirehathaway.com%2Fletters%2F2010ltr.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E2010%20letter%20to%20shareholders%3C%2Fa%3E)%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BAnybody%20that%20knows%20where%20they're%20going%20to%20want%20to%20live%2C%20and%20has%20a%20reasonably%20assured%20income%2C%20I%20think%20they're%20making%20a%20terrible%20mistake%20if%20they%20don't%20buy%20a%20single-family%20home%20now%20and%20get%20a%20mortgage%20at%20these%20rates%20%E2%80%94%20and%20they%20should%20get%20a%2030-year%20mortgage.%20It's%20really%20a%20golden%20opportunity.%20You're%20not%20going%20to%20see%20a%20chance%20like%20this%20five%20years%20from%20now%2C%20I'll%20guarantee%20you%20that.%26quot%3B%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbuffett.cnbc.com%2Fvideo%2F2012%2F10%2F24%2Fbuffett-no-question-the-global-economy-is-slowing-full-interview.html%3F%26start%3D3758%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECNBC%20interview%20in%202012%3C%2Fa%3E)%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20know%20you're%20going%20to%20live%20in%20a%20given%20area%2C%20or%20think%20it's%20very%20likely%2C%20for%20a%20considerable%20period%20of%20time%20and%20you've%20got%20a%20family%2C%20the%20home%20is%20terrific.%26quot%3B%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbc.com%2F2017%2F03%2F06%2Fheres-why-warren-buffett-thinks-you-should-buy-a-home.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECNBC%20interview%2C%202017%3C%2Fa%3E)%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BA%20home's%20a%20wonderful%20thing%2C%20but%20I%20wouldn't%20buy%20one%20if%20I%20was%20going%20to%20move%20in%20six%20months%2C%20and%20I%20wouldn't%20buy%20one%20if%20I%20was%20terribly%20nervous%20about%20my%20job.%26quot%3B%20(2012%20interview)%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BA%20house%20can%20be%20a%20nightmare%20if%20the%20buyer's%20eyes%20are%20bigger%20than%20his%20wallet%20and%20if%20a%20lender%20%E2%80%94%20often%20protected%20by%20a%20government%20guarantee%20%E2%80%94%20facilitates%20his%20fantasy.%20Our%20country's%20social%20goal%20should%20not%20be%20to%20put%20families%20into%20the%20house%20of%20their%20dreams%2C%20but%20rather%20to%20put%20them%20into%20a%20house%20they%20can%20afford.%26quot%3B%20(2010%20letter)%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBuffett%20described%20a%2030-year%20mortgage%20as%20%26quot%3Bthe%20best%20instrument%20in%20the%20world.%20Because%20if%20you're%20wrong%20and%20rates%20go%20to%202%25%2C%20which%20I%20don't%20think%20they%20will%2C%20you%20pay%20it%20off.%20It's%20a%20one-way%20renegotiation.%20It%20is%20an%20incredibly%20attractive%20instrument%20for%20the%20homeowner%2C%20and%20you've%20got%20a%20one-way%20bet.%26quot%3B%20(2017%20interview)%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Fol%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwarren-buffett-homebuying-owning-home-quotes-berkshire-hathaway-investing-wealth-2024-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720267562000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F668801b81f0c1cd6d731c1f0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwarren-buffett-homebuying-owning-home-quotes-berkshire-hathaway-investing-wealth-2024-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Warren%20Buffett%20joked%20about%20his%20%26quot%3Blove%20affair%26quot%3B%20with%20his%20home%2C%20called%20it%20his%20%26quot%3Bthird-best%20investment%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20warned%20the%20wron