2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EHon'ble%20President%20of%20India%2C%20on%20the%20recommendation%20of%20Government%20of%20India%2C%20has%20approved%20the%20proposal%20for%20summoning%20of%20both%20the%20Houses%20of%20Parliament%20for%20the%20Budget%20Session%2C%202024%20from%2022nd%20July%2C%202024%20to%2012%20August%2C%202024%20(Subject%20to%20exigencies%20of%20Parliamentary%20Business).%20Union%20Budget%2C%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Kiren%20Rijiju%20(%40KirenRijiju)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FKirenRijiju%2Fstatus%2F1809529286744739908%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJuly%206%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHon'ble%20President%20of%20India%2C%20on%20the%20recommendation%20of%20Government%20of%20India%2C%20has%20approved%20the%20proposal%20for%20summoning%20of%20both%20the%20Houses%20of%20Parliament%20for%20the%20Budget%20Session%2C%202024%20from%2022nd%20July%2C%202024%20to%2012%20August%2C%202024%20(Subject%20to%20exigencies%20of%20Parliamentary%20Business).%20Union%20Budget%2C%202024-25%20will%20be%20presented%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20on%2023%20July%2C%202024%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20minister%20posted%20on%20X.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFinance%20Minister%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman%20had%20presented%20the%20interim%20Budget%20in%20February%20in%20view%20of%20the%20upcoming%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%20She%20will%20be%20presenting%20her%20seventh%20consecutive%20Budget%2C%20becoming%20the%20first%20finance%20minister%20in%20India's%20history%20to%20do%20so%2C%20surpassing%20the%20previous%20record%20set%20by%20Morarji%20Desai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20will%20be%20the%20first%20Budget%20presented%20during%20Narendra%20Modi's%20third%20term%20as%20Prime%20Minister%20and%20also%20the%20first%20under%20him%20in%20which%20the%20BJP%20does%20not%20have%20a%20majority%20on%20its%20own.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExpectations%20from%20the%20Budget%20have%20been%20high%20and%20were%20fuelled%20further%20when%20President%20Droupadi%20Murmu%20said%20in%20her%20joint%20address%20that%20it%20will%20see%20%26quot%3Bmany%20historic%20steps%26quot%3B%20and%20accelerate%20the%20pace%20of%20reforms.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20Budget%20will%20be%20an%20effective%20document%20of%20the%20government's%20far-reaching%20policies%20and%20futuristic%20vision.%20Along%20with%20major%20economic%20and%20social%20decisions%2C%20many%20historic%20steps%20will%20also%20be%20seen%20in%20this%20Budget...%20%26quot%3BThe%20pace%20of%20reforms%20will%20be%20further%20accelerated%20in%20tune%20with%20the%20aspirations%20of%20people%20of%20India%20for%20rapid%20development%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20had%20said%20on%20June%2027.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20middle%20and%20salaried%20classes%2C%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20expectations%20is%20that%20there%20will%20be%20a%20change%20in%20the%20income%20tax%20structure%20which%20will%20leave%20more%20disposable%20income%20in%20their%20hands.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EStormy%20Session%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20special%20session%20of%20the%20Parliament%2C%20the%20first%20in%20the%2018th%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20witnessed%20stormy%20scenes%20with%20the%20strengthened%20opposition%20looking%20to%20make%20its%20presence%20felt%20under%20the%20new%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20in%20the%20House%2C%20Rahul%20Gandhi.%20In%20the%20general%20elections%2C%20the%20results%20for%20which%20were%20declared%20on%20June%204%2C%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20won%20232%20seats%20and%20restricted%20the%20BJP%20to%20240.%20The%20NDA%2C%20though%2C%20has%20a%20comfortable%20majority%20with%20293%20MPs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NEET%20paper%20leak%20exam%20issue%2C%20Manipur%2C%20Emergency%2C%20Agnipath%20scheme%20and%20the%20alleged%20undermining%20of%20the%20Constitution%20by%20the%20ruling%20dispensation%20dominated%20the%20special%20session%20and%20are%20likely%20to%20make%20their%20presence%20felt%20in%20the%20Budget%20session%20as%20well.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720264200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2F2u5625g_nirmala-sitharaman-budget-2024-live_625x300_01_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffinance-minister-nirmala-sitharaman-to-present-modi-3-0-budget-on-july-23-6046993%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20full%20Budget%20for%20the%20year%202024-25%20will%20be%20presented%20on%20July%2023%2C%20with%20the%20Parliament%20session%20beginning%20a%20day%20earlier%2C%20Union%20Minister%20Kiren%20Rijiju%20announced%20on%20Saturday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffinance-minister-nirmala-sitharaman-to-present-modi-3-0-budget-on-july-23-6046993%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffinance-minister-nirmala-sitharaman-to-present-modi-3-0-budget-on-july-23-6046993%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffinance-minister-nirmala-sitharaman-to-present-modi-3-0-budget-on-july-23-6046993%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Cops%20Probe%20Political%20Links%20Of%20Bhole%20Baba%20After%20Killer%20Hathras%20Stampede%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E121%20families%20have%20still%20been%20reeling%20under%20the%20impact%20of%20the%20stampede%20in%20Hathras%20on%20Tuesday%20where%20their%20loved%20ones%20died.%20But%20all%20of%20them%20have%20united%20in%20two%20demands%20-%20a%20swift%20probe%2C%20and%20action%20against%20Bhole%20Baba%20aka%20Suraj%20Pal%20Singh%20who%20organised%20the%20'satsang'%20where%20the%20stampede%20occurred.%20After%20arresting%20several%20accused%20in%20the%20case%2C%20police%20have%20uncovered%20that%20Bhole%20Baba's%20organisation%20had%20been%20getting%20funding%20from%20several%20political%20parties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHathras%20Superintendent%20of%20Police%2C%20Nipun%20Agarwal%2C%20today%20revealed%20that%20the%20main%20accused%20Devprakash%20Madhukar%20had%20recently%20been%20in%20contact%20with%20several%20political%20parties.%20This%20has%20prompted%20investigations%20into%20potential%20political%20conspiracies%20surrounding%20the%20incident.%20Madhukar%20was%20known%20to%20manage%20fundraising%20activities%20for%20events%20organized%20by%20the%20self-styled%20godman.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Agarwal%20emphasized%20that%20financial%20transactions%2C%20money%20trails%2C%20and%20call%20records%20associated%20with%20Madhukar%20are%20currently%20under%20scrutiny.%20The%20police%20are%20also%20planning%20to%20seek%20his%20remand%20for%20further%20questioning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20initial%20probe%20into%20the%20stampede%20had%20revealed%20that%20the%20godman%20had%20received%20permission%20to%20host%20an%20event%20for%2080%2C000%20people%2C%20but%202.5%20lakh%20people%20were%20allowed%20to%20enter%20the%20venue.%20After%20the%20gathering%2C%20when%20the%20'godman'%20was%20leaving%2C%20there%20was%20a%20rush%20among%20his%20followers%20to%20collect%20dust%20stirred%20up%20by%20his%20car's%20tyres.%20According%20to%20officials%2C%20the%20godman's%20private%20security%20guards%20started%20pushing%20his%20followers%20and%20some%20people%20fell%20and%20were%20trampled.%20In%20the%20chaos%2C%20many%20others%20fled%20towards%20the%20open%20field%20and%20slipped%2C%20and%20others%20ran%20over%20them.%20Many%20of%20those%20killed%20in%20the%20stampede%20were%20women%20and%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20eyewitnesses%2C%20only%20about%2040%20police%20personnel%20were%20on%20duty%20to%20ensure%20safety%20at%20this%20massive%20gathering%20and%20they%20were%20overwhelmed%20when%20the%20stampede%20broke%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMadhukar%20was%20the%20'mukhya%20sevadar'%20(chief%20of%20security)%20of%20the%20'satsang'%20where%20the%20stampede%20occurred.%20He%20is%20the%20only%20accused%20named%20in%20the%20FIR%20lodged%20at%20Sikandra%20Rao%20police%20station%20in%20Hathras%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20incident%2C%20and%20Suraj%20Pal%20Singh%20hasn't%20been%20named.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInitially%2C%20Madhukar's%20lawyer%2C%20AP%20Singh%2C%20had%20asserted%20that%20his%20client%20had%20voluntarily%20surrendered%20to%20the%20Delhi%20police%20for%20medical%20treatment.%20However%2C%20Hathras%20police%20said%20they%20arrested%20Madhukar%20through%20technical%20surveillance%2C%20offering%20a%20reward%20of%20one%20lakh%20rupees%20for%20information%20leading%20to%20his%20arrest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Saturday%20afternoon%2C%20amidst%20tight%20security%20arrangements%2C%20Madhukar%20was%20brought%20to%20the%20Bagla%20Combined%20District%20Hospital%20in%20Hathras%20for%20a%20medical%20examination.%20He%20appeared%20with%20his%20face%20covered%20by%20a%20handkerchief%20and%20a%20stole%20wrapped%20around%20his%20head.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20three-member%20judicial%20commission%20team%20has%20arrived%20in%20Hathras%20to%20investigate%20administrative%20lapses%20that%20may%20have%20contributed%20to%20the%20tragedy.%20Statements%20from%20multiple%20officials%20have%20been%20recorded%2C%20and%20the%20team%20visited%20the%20site%20of%20the%20incident%20to%20gather%20further%20evidence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAuthorities%20plan%20to%20delve%20deeper%20into%20Madhukar's%20association%20with%20Bhole%20Baba's%20trust%2C%20scrutinizing%20funding%20sources%20and%20bank%20accounts.%20They%20intend%20to%20collaborate%20with%20other%20agencies%20to%20probe%20potential%20political%20links%20to%20the%20case.%20Should%20it%20be%20deemed%20necessary%2C%20a%20summons%20may%20also%20be%20issued%20to%20Bhole%20Baba%20for%20questioning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20conducting%20a%20thorough%20investigation%20into%20Madhukar's%20background%20and%20his%20role%20in%20the%20incident%2C%26quot%3B%20stated%20SP%20Nipun%20Agarwal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20any%20political%20is%20found%20to%20be%20associated%20with%20(Bhole%20Baba's)%20organisation%2C%20we%20will%20take%20action%20against%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20if%20the%20self-styled%20godman%20may%20be%20arrested%2C%20state%20police%20chief%20Prashant%20Kumar%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BRight%20now%2C%20everything%20is%20a%20matter%20of%20investigation.%20We%20do%20not%20want%20to%20influence%20the%20investigation%20by%20drawing%20any%20immediate%20conclusion.%20The%20ambit%20of%20the%20investigation%20is%20open.%20Action%20will%20be%20taken%20based%20on%20the%20facts%20that%20come%20to%20light%20during%20the%20investigation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720264080000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Fdqk93dl4_hathras-stampede_625x300_06_July_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhathras-stampede-funding-cops-probe-political-links-of-bhole-baba-after-killer-hathras-stampede-6047283%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22121%20families%20have%20still%20been%20reeling%20under%20the%20impact%20of%20the%20stampede%20in%20Hathras%20on%20Tuesday%20where%20their%20loved%20ones%20died.%20But%20all%20of%20them%20have%20united%20in%20two%20demands%20-%20a%20swift%20probe%2C%20and%20action%20against%20Bhole%20Baba.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhathras-stampede-funding-cops-probe-political-links-of-bhole-baba-after-killer-hathras-stampede-6047283%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhathras-stampede-funding-cops-probe-political-links-of-bhole-baba-after-killer-hathras-stampede-6047283%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhathras-stampede-funding-cops-probe-political-links-of-bhole-baba-after-killer-hathras-stampede-6047283%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Tornadoes%20kill%205%2C%20injure%2083%20in%20China's