0and%20flowers%20on%20his%20terrace%20farm.%20And%20the%20best%20part%3F%20He%20only%20uses%20organic%20fertilisers%20and%20techniques%20such%20as%20hydroponics%20to%20farm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%20is%20all%20you%20need%20to%20know%20about%20this%20humble%20farmer%E2%80%99s%20magnificent%20farm%20%E2%80%93%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98All%20I%20have%20is%20a%20terrace%E2%80%99%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBorn%20in%20a%20small%20village%20in%20Udupi%2C%20Lobo%20grew%20up%20in%20a%20farming%20family.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20all%20I%20had%20known%20for%20most%20of%20my%20childhood.%20I%20had%20always%20been%20interested%20in%20farming%20and%20felt%20a%20connection%20with%20plants%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20you%20might%20find%20it%20odd%20that%20a%20youngster%20wanted%20to%20take%20up%20farming%20as%20a%20profession%2C%20it%20was%20all%20Lobo%20had%20ever%20wanted.%20%E2%80%9CI%20had%20wanted%20to%20try%20out%20new%20ways%20of%20growing%20plants%20effectively%20and%20profitably.%20I%20knew%20getting%20into%20the%20profession%20that%20it%20is%20more%20passion-driven%20than%20profit%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20continues%2C%20%E2%80%9CHowever%2C%20my%20family%20land%20was%20stuck%20in%20a%20conflict%20and%20I%20could%20not%20farm%20on%20it.%20We%20come%20from%20humble%20backgrounds%20and%20those%20lands%20were%20our%20only%20support.%20My%20dream%20seemed%20to%20be%20out%20of%20reach%20for%20a%20moment%20but%20I%20decided%20to%20keep%20going.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Flobo-1-1719992669.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Lobo%20grows%20200%20varieties%20of%20plants%20on%20his%20terrace%20garden%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media