e%20stand%20out%3F%20It%E2%80%99s%20completely%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F242588%2Fkarnataka-first-recycled-plastic-brick-walls-roof-house-construction-cost-company-architect-plans-how-to-san196%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emade%20using%20plastic%3C%2Fa%3E!%20Yes%2C%20plastic%20%E2%80%94%20right%20from%20the%20floor%20tiles%2C%20doors%2C%20and%20walls%20to%20stairs%20and%20ceiling!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBuilt%20by%20Dr%20Balmukund%20Paliwal%2C%20the%20house%20is%20spread%20across%20625%20sq%20ft%2C%2018%20feet%20in%20height%20and%2010%20feet%20wide.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20made%20each%20and%20every%20part%20of%20the%20house%20from%20plastic.%20For%20this%2C%20we%20utilised%20all%20kinds%20of%20plastic%20waste%20%E2%80%94%20including%20potato%20chips%20packets%2C%20water%20bottles%2C%20medicine%20wrappers%2C%20cosmetics%20bottles%2C%20and%20milk%20pouches%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConstructed%20under%20the%20guidance%20of%20Zila%20Parishad%20Chandrapur%2C%20this%20house%20has%20diverted%2013%20tonnes%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F310831%2Faurangabad-duo-build-eco-friendly-mud-home-with-plastic-bottle-walls-sustainable%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eplastic%20from%20ending%20up%20in%20landfills%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FTransformation-1720103262.gif%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-355684%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%E2%80%99s%20more%2C%20this%20plastic%20house%20is%20also%20portable.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20can%20dismantle%20it%20and%20assemble%20it%20within%20two%20to%20five%20hours%20just%20by%20operating%20the%20screws%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%2C%20adding