ttps%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fplastic-house-1-1720100210-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fplastic-house-1-1720100210-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fplastic-house-1-1720100210-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-355660%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20house%20is%20currently%20being%20used%20by%20tourists%20and%20breastfeeding%20mothers%20visiting%20the%20garden.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20years%2C%20concrete%20has%20been%20putting%20roofs%20over%20the%20heads%20of%20billions.%20After%20water%2C%20concrete%20is%20the%20most%20widely%20used%20substance%20on%20Earth.%20Concrete%20is%20a%20thirsty%20behemoth%2C%20sucking%20up%20almost%20a%20tenth%20of%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20industrial%20water%20use.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20the%20cement%20industry%20were%20a%20country%2C%20it%20would%20be%20the%20third%20largest%20carbon%20dioxide%20emitter%20in%20the%20world%20with%20up%20to%202.8bn%20tonnes%2C%20surpassed%20only%20by%20China%20and%20the%20US%2C%E2%80%9D%20mentions%20a%20report%20published%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fcities%2F2019%2Ffeb%2F25%2Fconcrete-the-most-destructive-material-on-earth%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Guardian%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20also%20quoted%20concrete%20as%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20most%20destructive%20material%20to%20Earth.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Balmukund%20says%20he%20was%20inspired%20to%20tackle%20plastic%20waste%20in%202014%20when%20the%20Swachhata%20Bharat%20Abhiyan%20was%20launched.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20also%20inspired%20by%20my%20mother.%20Back%20in%20the%2060s%2C%20she%20used%20to%20wear%20polyester%20sarees.%20She%20would%20burn%20worn-out%20sarees.%20When%20polyester%20burns%2C%20it%20gives%20a%20plasticy%20smell%20and%20the%20fabric%20melts%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CShe%20would%20mix%20the%20molten%20fabric%20with%20ash%20from%20%3Cem%3Echulha%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20make%20a%20thick%20paste.%20She%20would%20apply%20the%20semi-solid%20substance%20onto%20a%20bamboo%20%3Cem%3Esoop%3C%2Fem%3E%20(traditional%20tray)%20to%20make%20it%20rigid.%20This%20would%20increase%20its%20durability%20from%20a%20year%20to%20four%20years.%20Later%20on%2C%20she%20started%20using%20it%20to%20fix%20broken%20pans%20and%20drums.%20She%20never%20went%20to%20school%20but%20I%20learnt%20a%20lot%20from%20her%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20mother%E2%80%99s%20innovative%20ways%20of%20reusing%20plastic%20remained%20with%20Dr%20Balmukund.%20He%20utilised%20this%20concept%20in%20the%20construction%20of%20his%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F143206%2Fhyderabad-office-recycled-plastic-waste-bamboo-bamboo-house-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eplastic%20house%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewhen%20IAS%20Vivek%20Johnson%2C%20chief%20executive%20officer%2C%20Zila%20Parishad%2C%20reached%20out%20to%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201600px)%20100vw%2C%201600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-07-05-at-10.24.01-AM_11zon-1-1720155956.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20house%20was%20constructed%20under%20the%20guidance%20of%20Zila%20Parishad%20Chandrapur.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-07-05-at-10.24.01-AM_11zon-1-1720155956.jpeg%201600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-07-05-at-10.24.01-AM_11zon-1-1720155956-300x225.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-07-05-at-10.24.01-AM_11zon-1-1720155956-500x375.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-07-05-at-10.24.01-AM_11zon-1-1720155956-768x576.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-07-05-at-10.24.01-AM_11zon-1-1720155956-1536x1152.jpeg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-07-05-at-10.24.01-AM_11zon-1-1720155956-150x113.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-355693%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20house%20was%20constructed%20under%20the%20guidance%20of%20Zila%20Parishad%20Chandrapur.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20IAS%20officer%20shares%2C%20%E2%80%9CAs%20part%20of%20the%20mandate%20of%20the%20Zila%20Parishad%2C%20we%20are%20required%20to%20build%20a%20demo%20house%20for%20Awas%20Yojana.%20We%20didn%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20use%20reinforced%20concrete%20and%20that%E2%80%99s%20when%20I%20met%20Paliwal%20sir.%20I%20knew%20he%20produces%20bars%20from%20plastic%20waste%2C%20which%20can%20be%20moulded%20into%20articles.%20With%20our%20vision%20of%20a%20futuristic%20house%20and%20Paliwal%20sir%E2%80%99s%20efforts%2C%20we%20were%20able%20to%20design%20an%20innovative%20model%20house.%20This%20will%20inspire%20people%20to%20make%20homes%20from%20plastic.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHouse%20made%20from%20chips%20packets%2C%20broken%20mugs%20and%20bottles%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStarting%20early%20this%20year%2C%20Dr%20Balmukund%20segregated%20and%20collected%20plastic%20waste%20like%20chips%20packets%2C%20shampoo%20bottles%2C%20and%20broken%20plastic%20mugs%20from%20dumping%20grounds%20in%20the%20city.%20After%20drying%20them%20naturally%2C%20he%20shredded%20them%20into%20pellets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fplastic-house-2-1720100452.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22It%E2%80%99s%20completely%20made%20using%20plastic%20%E2%80%94%20right%20from%20the%20floor%20tiles%2C%20doors%2C%20and%20walls%20to%20stairs%20and%20ceiling!%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fplastic-house-2-1720100452.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fplastic-house-2-1720100452-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fplastic-house-2-1720100452-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fplastic-house-2-1720100452-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fplastic-house-2-1720100452-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-355661%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20house%20is%20completely%20made%20using%20plastic%20%E2%80%94%20right%20from%20the%20floor%20tiles%2C%20doors%2C%20and%20walls%20to%20the%20stairs%20and%20roof!%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20pellets%20are%20melted%20into%20a%20semi-solid%20substance%20through%20an%20extruder.%20This%20substance%20can%20thus%20be%20moulded%20into%20any%20shape%2C%20like%20doors%2C%20legs%20of%20a%20bench%2C%20tiles%2C%20etc.%20Thereafter%2C%20it%20is%20passed%20through%20a%20chiller%20and%20later%20on%2C%20polished%20and%20coloured%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20took%20Dr%20Balmukund%20three%20months%20to%20construct%20the%20plastic%20house.%20He%20has%20carved%20designs%20on%20the%20doors%20and%20beds%20in%20the%20house%20to%20give%20it%20a%20wooden%20look.%20%E2%80%9CSeeing%20the%20house%2C%20nobody%20can%20guess%20it%20is%20completely%20made%20of%20plastic%20waste.%20We%20have%20also%20used%20an%20additional%202.5%20tonnes%20of%20steel%20for%20rigid%20support%20and%20framework%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharing%20more%20about%20the%20features%20of%20the%20house%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThis%20house%20can%20be%20used%20in%20areas%20which%20are%20prone%20to%20electric%20shock%20or%20extreme%20hot%20and%20cold.%20As%20it%20is%20made%20from%20plastic%2C%20it%20provides%20insulation%20from%20outside%20weather.%20The%20house%20is%20comparatively%20three%20to%20four%20degrees%20cooler%20than%20outside%20temperatures%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CCompared%20to%20a%20cement%20home%2C%20you%20do%20not%20require%20any%20water%20to%20construct%20a%20plastic%20house.%20Also%2C%20in%20reinforced%20concrete%2C%20percolation%20and%20cracks%20will%20eventually%20occur%2C%20but%20in%20a%20plastic%20home%2C%20there%20won%E2%80%99t%20be%20any%20cracks.%20The%20reinforced%20cemented%20structures%20require%20maintenance%20in%2020%20to%2025%20years%20but%20no%20such%20maintenance%20is%20needed%20in%20structures%20made%20of%20plastic%2C%20which%20can%20last%20for%20decades%2C%20even%20after%20your%20lifetime%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20claims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FInfographic-website-15-1720100001.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22How%20to%20build%20a%20plastic%20house%3F%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FInfographic-website-15-1720100001.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FInfographic-website-15-1720100001-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FInfographic-website-15-1720100001-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FInfographic-website-15-1720100001-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FInfographic-website-15-1720100001-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-355657%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20the%20safety%20risks%2C%20Dr%20Balmukund%20shares%2C%20%E2%80%9CThis%20house%20is%20rust-free%2C%20fireproof%2C%20and%20shock-free.%20Usually%2C%20plastic%20melts%20at%20around%20250%20degrees%20and%20requires%20above%20300%20degrees%20for%20it%20to%20burn.%20Wooden%20homes%20catch%20fire%20faster%20than%20a%20plastic%20house%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20informs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CChandrapur%20city%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20polluted%20cities%20as%20it%20is%20an%20industrial%20area%20with%20mines%2C%20cement%20and%20explosives%20factories.%20We%20stressed%20on%20ways%20to%20reduce%20pollution.%20Dr%20Paliwal%20pitched%20in%20to%20design%20a%20house%20made%20of%20plastic.%20Although%20I%20was%20very%20doubtful%2C%20he%20was%20very%20confident.%20Let%20alone%20the%20public%2C%20even%20I%20was%20surprised%20to%20see%20the%20final%20house.%20When%20it%20was%20inaugurated%2C%20the%20District%20Magistrate%20and%20Chief%20Minister%20also%20could%20not%20believe%20their%20eyes%2C%E2%80%9D%20IAS%20Vivek%20Johnson%20tells%3Cstrong%3E%20The%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20a%20demo%20house%20which%20can%20be%20replicated%20in%20the%20housing%20scheme%20under%20the%20Pradhan%20Mantri%20Awas%20Yojana.%20By%20constructing%20such%20homes%2C%20tonnes%20of%20plastic%20waste%20from%20villages%20and%20cities%20can%20be%20utilised.%20In%20future%2C%20if%20you%20ever%20desire%20to%20dismantle%20the%20house%2C%20you%20can%20reuse%20and%20recycle%20all%20the%20demolished%20plastic%20material%2C%20which%20is%20not%20possible%20in%20reinforced%20concrete%20structures.%20By%20adopting%20such%20a%20house%2C%20you%20protect%20the%20environment%2C%20use%20less%20natural%20resources%2C%20reduce%20plastic%20waste%2C%20and%20generate%20employment%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Dr%20Balmukund.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIncluding%20collection%2C%20machinery%2C%20and%20labour%2C%20the%20cost%20of%20constructing%20the%20plastic%20house%20was%20Rs%209%20lakh%2C%20claims%20the%20doctor.%20Of%20the%20total%20cost%2C%20the%20Zila%20Parishad%20sanctioned%20Rs%205%20lakh%20(the%20upper%20limit%20for%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20demo%20house).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20comparatively%2020%20percent%20less%20than%20the%20conventional%20cemented%20house.%20I%20invested%20the%20remaining%20amount%20so%20that%20funds%20do%20not%20become%20an%20issue%20and%20we%20have%20an%20example%20for%20others%20to%20adopt.%20As%20citizens%2C%20we%20need%20to%20understand%20our%20responsibilities%20towards%20protecting%20the%20environment.%20I%20am%20doing%20my%20bit%2C%20and%20I%20seek%20public%20and%20Government%20support%20to%20promote%20such%20houses%20to%20benefit%20all%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20concludes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20All%20photos%3A%20Dr%20Balmukund%20Paliwal.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720102772000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fplastic-house-2-1720100452.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D355647%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Dr%20Balmukund%20Paliwal%20built%20a%20two-storey%20house%20in%20Chandrapur%2C%20Maharashtra%2C%20using%20recycled%20plastic%20waste%20and%20preventing%2013%20tonnes%20of%20plastic%20from%20reaching%20landfills.%20Here's%20how%20he%20did%20it.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A27%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F355647%2Fdr-balmukund-paliwal-builds-plastic-house-chandrapur-maharashtra-