20them%20safety%2C%20education%20and%20food.%20We%20found%20that%20the%20best%20way%20to%20do%20this%20would%20be%20through%20a%20daycare%20and%20playschool%20centre%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Meghana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBuilt%20at%20construction%20sites%2C%20these%20centres%20are%20spread%20over%20half%20an%20acre.%20They%20have%20an%20indoor%20and%20outdoor%20play%20area%2C%20classrooms%2C%20audio-visual%20rooms%20and%20much%20more.%20Teachers%20from%20Meru%20International%20School%20built%20a%20basic%20to%20advanced%20curriculum%20that%20would%20focus%20on%20languages%2C%20numeracy%2C%20physical%20activity%2C%20arts%20and%20crafts%2C%20as%20well%20as%20health%20and%20hygiene%20skills%2C%20depending%20upon%20the%20age%20of%20the%20kids.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOpen%20from%208%3A30%20am%20to%203%3A30%20pm%2C%20each%20day%20starts%20with%20circle%20time%2C%20indoor%20playtime%2C%20toilet%20breaks%20(to%20inculcate%20good%20habits)%2C%20English%2C%20Hindi%2C%20and%20Math%20classes%2C%20along%20with%20audio-visual%20aids%20(music%2Fdance%2Fmovies%2Fstorytelling%2Fart)%2C%20and%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20biggest%20challenge%20was%20convincing%20the%20parents.%20Only%20after%20the%20parents%20accompanied%20the%20children%20to%20the%20centre%20daily%20did%20they%20understand%20the%20benefits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20counsel%20the%20parents%20on%20the%20importance%20of%20early%20education.%20Our%20idea%20is%20to%20create%20a%20habit%20of%20coming%20to%20a%20structured%20space%20daily.%20After%20attending%20this%20centre%20for%20two%20or%20three%20years%2C%20they%20will%20be%20ready%20to%20join%20a%20mainstream%20school%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Meghana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20many%20interventions%20which%20impressed%20on%20the%20importance%20of%20education%2C%20children%20started%20attending%20the%20centre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20basics%20of%20early%20childhood%20education%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEach%20centre%20has%20a%20ca