0%9CI%20never%20replied%20back%20to%20any%20taunts%20but%20patiently%20waited%20for%20the%20results.%20And%2021%20months%20later%2C%20we%20earned%20Rs%201.25%20crore%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20smiles.%20Today%2C%20Gaurav%20has%20expanded%20freshwater%20pearl%20farming%20in%20three%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F342922%2Fhow-to-do-pearl-farming-in-artificial-ponds-in-rajasthan-computer-teacher-reaps-huge-profits%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eponds%20in%20Rajasthan%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20two%20ponds%20in%20West%20Bengal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20started%20freshwater%20pearl%20farming%20to%20earn%20an%20income%20for%20myself%20but%20this%20has%20also%20helped%20me%20establish%20an%20identity%20by%20doing%20unique%20work.%20Besides%2C%20this%20work%20has%20become%20an%20income%20source%20for%20other%20small%20farmers%20who%20invested%20in%20this%20project.%20It%20was%20better%20than%20investing%20in%20mutual%20funds%20or%20fixed%20deposits.%20It%20was%20so%20fulfilling%20to%20see%20the%20results%20because%20it%20shaped%20my%20career%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20All%20photos%3A%20Gaurav%20Pachauri.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719845248000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpearl-farming-1-1719841061.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D355072%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Gaurav%20Pachauri%20took%20up%20freshwater%20pearl%20farming%20after%20failing%20to%20crack%20government%20exams%20for%20four%20years.%20He%20set%20up%20a%20pearl%20farm%20in%20Bharatpur%2C%20Rajasthan%2C%20earning%20Rs%2055%20lakh%20within%2021%20months.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F355072%2Ffreshwater-pearl-farming-help-local-farmers-earn-lakhs-gaurav-pachauri-bh