%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20this%2C%20Sumila%20says%2C%20she%20makes%20an%20average%20sale%20of%20Rs%2020%20lakh%20in%20a%20month.%20Interestingly%2C%20delivering%20through%20her%20website%2C%20she%20has%20developed%20a%20customer%20base%20in%20the%20United%20States%2C%20the%20United%20Kingdom%2C%20Australia%2C%20and%20Malaysia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20homemaker%20to%20an%20entrepreneur%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.pharmacognosyasia.com%2FFiles%2FOther%2FAJPV5I4p0519.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E2021%20study%20%3C%2Fa%3Epublished%20in%20the%20Asian%20Journal%20of%20Pharmacognosy%20termed%20virgin%20coconut%20oil%20as%20a%20%E2%80%98miracle%20oil%E2%80%99.%20The%20study%20mentions%20that%20the%20oil%20has%20antioxidant%2C%20anti-inflammatory%2C%20and%20immunomodulatory%2C%20anti-hyperlipidemia%2C%20anticancer%2C%20antidiabetic%2C%20anti-bacterial%20and%20neuroprotective%20properties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESumila%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CVirgin%20coconut%20oil%20is%20considered%20the%20mother%20of%20all%20oils%20owing%20to%20its%20health%20benefits.%20There%20is%20a%20lot%20of%20goodness%20in%20it.%20It%20also%20acts%20as%20an%20immunity%20booster%20and%20is%20the%20best%20moisturiser.%20Mothers%20can%20even%20apply%20the%20oil%20on%20newborn%20babies.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FSumila-2-1719576057.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sumila%20believes%20launching%20her%20own%20company%20was%20a%20turning%20point%20for%20her.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FSumila-2-1719576057.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FSumila-